attributes.title: This app made me violently poop my pants
attributes.review: As soon as I started to download the app I felt a vile sensation in my stomach, and I’m used to having some bad boys but this was something else, something disastrous. Fearing for my pants I ran to the bathroom to try to save the last of my very little dignity, but it was too late, the runs had begun. Just as I opened the door I felt a fiery explosion erupt from my gluteus. Hot molten digested food from my night before began to pour out of my pants onto the floor. I desperately tried to leap onto the toilet, but my attempts were all in vain. I slipped in my own creation and felt the warmth of the half liquid, half chimichanga splash onto me. I knew that it must’ve been the app, nothing like this had ever happened before. Donny, how could you do this to me? I crawled to my phone, brown spraying out of me like a magnificent fountain brought to life after years of being condemned. I desperately tried to avoid the still growing puddle underneath my body but to no avail. Grabbing my phone off the ledge I opened it and immediately deleted the app. Then, just as it had come, it was gone. I’ve never felt such a wave of relief wash over me. But the damage had been done. I lied there, in my own misery and bowels and cried. Never again will I trust this app or any like it.
